additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: INGREDIENTS: Sow Stall Free Australian Pork (92%), BBQ Seasoning (3.5%) (Maize Maltodextrin, Rice Flour, Dextrose, Onion, Spices and Spice Extracts (Pepper, Paprika, Cumin), Garlic, Salt, Oregano), Water, Salt, Seaweed Extract, Tapioca Starch, Bamboo Fibre, Yeast Extract, Flax Seed Fibre, Rosemary Extract, Spice Extracts (Rosemary, Jalapeno), Smoke Flavouring.

description: Coles Slow Cooked Pulled Pork, 250g. This pork shoulder has been lightly seasoned with a touch of BQQ seasoning, slow cooked and pulled to create tender and tasty pork ready to eat in burgers or tacos.
name: Slow Cooked Pulled Pork
